1
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:45,000
The 13th year of the Chenghua reign

2
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:48,200
At the proposal of Eunuch Wang Zhi and Consort Wan,

3
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:51,200
Emperor Xianzong of Ming established the Western Depot alongside the Eastern Depot,

4
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:56,560
collectively known as the Secret Guard along with the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

5
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,520
What is unbelievable is that

6
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,680
the true core members of the Secret Guard

7
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:06,520
are composed of civilians whose backgrounds, names,

8
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,040
and even age information

9
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:10,520
are kept strictly confidential.

10
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,680
Reaching limits unbearable for ordinary people,

11
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:15,600
in terms of mental and physical training requirements.

12
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:19,320
They are required to master literature and etiquette,

13
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,320
multiple languages,

14
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:22,720
martial arts,

15
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,600
illusions,

16
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:24,520
medicine,

17
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,640
mechanics,

18
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,080
the Art of Qimen Dunjia,

19
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,600
as well as gambling and deception,

20
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,560
and even the varied seduction arts of courtesans.

21
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:34,280
Thus allowing the Secret Guard's scope of activity

22
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:37,240
to span from the capital to all regions to gather intelligence.

23
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:40,320
From commoners to high-ranking court officials,

24
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,560
everyone lives in

25
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,760
the fear of being dominated

26
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,520
by the secretive Secret Guard.

27
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,080
Standing tall like a mountain.

28
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,800
Flowing with the river.

29
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,640
A loyal heart and righteous blood.

30
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:33,000
No regrets in this life.

31
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,120
Lord Shen.

32
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,720
Everything is ready.

33
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:15,800
My Lord.

34
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,880
Retrieve the file of the guilty official Li Chenyang.

35
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,920
Extract him from the prison.

36
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,360
Escort him to the execution ground.

37
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,200
Yes, sir.

38
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,080
The Eastern Depot is supervising the execution today,

39
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:38,400
yet we from the Grand Court of Justice are waiting here wagging our tails.

40
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,040
Accompanying the Eastern Depot on duty,

41
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,360
if you don't watch your head,

42
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,160
the person being executed tomorrow

43
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,440
will be you and me.

44
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,720
Be more careful.

45
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,040
Executing a traitor

46
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,480
naturally makes everyone cheer.

47
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,920
But it happens to be the upright

48
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,480
Minister of War, Lord Li Chenyang.

49
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,520
Suddenly charged with fabricated crimes by the Eastern Depot.

50
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,640
Among the common people,

51
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,280
who isn't discussing

52
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,480
how they are covering up the truth?

53
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,760
Those who don't know the facts

54
00:04:59,080 --> 00:04:59,800
might think our Grand Court of Justice

55
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,120
is in cahoots with the Secret Guard.

56
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,360
Just shut your mouth.

57
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,560
Master Zhang.

58
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,360
Stand guard here.

59
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,480
Lord Li.

60
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,720
Do you have any requests?

61
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,680
I am hungry.

62
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,560
Could I trouble you, Master Zhang,

63
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:25,000
to get me two taels of jujube cake?

64
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,920
I would be eternally grateful.

65
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,080
No problem.

66
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:31,880
Watch him.

67
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:36,920
Hot and fragrant jujube cakes!

68
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:38,400
Next.

69
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,120
How many pieces?

70
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:40,680
Here you go.

71
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,320
Next. How many pieces do you want?

72
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,280
One piece.

73
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,360
One piece. Here.

74
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,400
Such a large coin?

75
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,720
Miss, I haven't given you your change yet.

76
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,320
I'll return it to her for you.

77
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,680
How many pieces do you want?

78
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:25,840
That Western Region lady is really bold.

79
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,200
Daring to put on such a show here.

80
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,520
If the Eastern Depot agents hear this,

81
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,440
she'll likely suffer physical torture.

82
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,960
They execute a Second Rank Minister of War just like that.

83
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,600
What do people like us have to fear?

84
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:37,680
Do you know

85
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,600
why Lord Li offended the Secret Guard?

86
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,120
Publicly, they say it's treason.

87
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,760
Privately, I heard he petitioned to clear the names

88
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,880
of the three hundred Divine Machine Battalion soldiers who died three years ago.

89
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,800
It seems the Secret Guard was involved.

90
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,080
As a result, the Grand Court of Justice hastily closed the case.

91
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,160
Make way.

92
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,600
Miss, your singing is busy yet orderly,

93
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,520
slow yet unbroken.

94
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,200
The puppets are somewhat different

95
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,200
from what one usually sees.

96
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,680
The craftsmanship is truly exquisite and ornate.

97
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,720
You flatter me, My Lord.

98
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,080
These tools of my trade

99
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,640
are naturally more precious than my life.

100
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,240
Life and death come and go,

101
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,560
like a disheveled puppet.

102
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,120
When the single thread breaks,

103
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,560
it falls freely and openly.

104
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,960
The life and death of a puppet

105
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,400
lie within the single thread in my hand.

106
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,120
Do you find it amusing, My Lord?

107
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,280
The world always says

108
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,880
that fools are kindred spirits to me.

109
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,360
We must chat more when there is time.

110
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,760
However,

111
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,760
one must keep one's life to do so, right?

112
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,080
Oh, My Lord,

113
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:57,240
all things are fated,

114
00:07:57,520 --> 00:08:00,800
nothing is up to man.

115
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,600
I still have the next act to perform.

116
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:07,440
Make way.

117
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,640
Did you buy it yet?

118
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,240
The Nuo opera has started over there.

119
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:11,320
Hurry up, let's go.

120
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,440
Look, quickly!

121
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,560
That's amazing.

122
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,000
They are performing so well.

123
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:41,360
It's nothing.

124
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:08,160
Good.

125
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:17,080
A kind heart brings beauty;

126
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,040
a sincere heart brings answers.

127
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,840
The plum blossom is noble and unsullied.

128
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,040
It rather suits Lord Li, who is to be executed today.

129
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,240
It matches his character well.

130
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,400
Perhaps

131
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,440
this plum branch wishes to suit the occasion

132
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,040
and bloom alone in the warm spring.

133
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,440
Sir.

134
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,360
Buy a branch?

135
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,200
Miss!

136
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:38,440
Miss!

137
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,560
Miss!

138
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:57,080
Miss!

139
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,720
The change from the jujube cake vendor...

140
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,400
you forgot to take it.

141
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:06,720
Sir,

142
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,120
money dropped on the ground...

143
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,120
do not turn back to pick it up.

144
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:11,280
It is bad luck.

145
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,160
Zhang Yi, Vice Minister of the Grand Court of Justice,

146
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,800
greets the Director of the Eastern Depot.

147
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:37,880
This is the imperial prison document.

148
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,400
Please review it, Director.

149
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:49,400
Director,

150
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:50,960
there are no issues with the document.

151
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,280
The execution can proceed immediately.

152
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:55,520
Usually, I am

153
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:58,120
before His Majesty, reviewing and stamping approvals.

154
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,040
Today,

155
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,800
this can be considered giving Li Chenyang

156
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,840
his final dignity.

157
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,640
Embroidered Uniform Guard, heed my order!

158
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:07,480
Here!

159
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,760
Strictly guard the supervision and execution platforms.

160
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:12,040
There must be no mistakes.

161
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,240
If the Grand Court of Justice wishes to do its part

162
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,040
in maintaining order among the commoners,

163
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,880
then I shall trouble you all to do so.

164
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,760
We are all officials of the fourth rank.

165
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,760
You are the Vice Minister of the Grand Court,

166
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,760
and he is a Commander.

167
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:39,640
He is merely flaunting his power to execute first and report later.

168
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,320
It is truly arrogant.

169
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,760
Where does all this resentment come from?

170
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,920
Just treat it as watching a play.

171
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,240
This is clearly treating our Grand Court of Justice

172
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,280
like mere ushers to order around!

173
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:49,240
Shut your mouth!

174
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,440
Execute him.

175
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:24,200
Lord Li!

176
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:25,160
We

177
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,400
shall go on ahead.

178
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:54,800
Through

179
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,560
the Eastern Depot's

180
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,240
thorough investigation,

181
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,480
the criminal official Li Chenyang,

182
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:03,040
holding the post of Minister of War,

183
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,600
has colluded with foreign vassals

184
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,000
and formed cliques for personal gain.

185
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,320
The evidence is irrefutable.

186
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:11,080
He has committed the gravest of the Ten Abominations.

187
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:13,480
He should be executed by lingering death.

188
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:16,440
However, in consideration of his past merits,

189
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:19,400
three feet of white silk shall be granted,

190
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,880
along with a carriage and a mat for the body,

191
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,280
to preserve his dignity.

192
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:32,880
Heaven is blind!

193
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:35,720
Heaven has eyes!

194
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,040
Heaven has eyes!

195
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,200
The time is now!

196
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,280
I, Li Chenyang,

197
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,800
bear a grievance

198
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:46,400
heavier than thousands of mountains!

199
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,880
To let me suffer this unrighted wrong,

200
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,760
with nowhere to seek justice!

201
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:51,640
What is that?

202
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:55,000
Dou E of the Yuan swore three oaths to prove her innocence.

203
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,400
Today,

204
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:59,720
I, Li Chenyang of the Ming, swear here and now!

205
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,560
May my blood splash three feet high,

206
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:05,240
and snow fall in the fourth month,

207
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:09,040
to restore

208
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,800
my innocence!

209
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:15,200
You confuse the masses with lies!

210
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,480
Execute him immediately!

211
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,640
Strong wine to honor Your Excellency.

212
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:25,520
May your spirit not blame me.

213
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:28,160
Follow the imps to the underworld.

214
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:31,160
Do not look back when you see the Judge.

215
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:33,480
The injustices and debts of this life

216
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,520
will be judged by the gods.

217
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:38,880
Go in peace to the afterlife.

218
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:45,480
Look, it's snowing!

219
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,400
It's snowing!

220
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,720
It's snowing!

221
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,360
It's really snowing!

222
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:49,000
Is there truly an injustice?

223
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,920
Is there an injustice?

224
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:01,560
There must be an injustice! It's an injustice!

225
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,720
His Excellency is a good official!

226
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:11,600
Even Heaven cannot watch this!

227
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:14,400
Innocent! Your Excellency is innocent!

228
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:17,600
Innocent! His Excellency is innocent!

229
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:29,320
The Way of Heaven is manifest!

230
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:34,640
What virtue do I, Li Chenyang, possess,

231
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:38,520
to receive such a clear sign from Heaven?

232
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,920
Even if I die,

233
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,240
I have no regrets.

234
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,800
You castrated villain!

235
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:55,200
Do you see this?

236
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:57,200
This is the Way of Heaven

237
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:58,760
punishing the likes of you!

238
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,400
Because of your selfish desires,

239
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:04,000
you destroyed the Divine Machine Battalion

240
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,920
and its three hundred warriors!

241
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:13,080
Sooner or later,

242
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:14,840
the truth will be known to all!

243
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:22,640
Innocent! Your Excellency is innocent!

244
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,800
Just you watch!

245
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:29,160
Why are you standing there?

246
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:32,880
Execute him!

247
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:35,680
Father!

248
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:37,080
The plum blossoms are blooming too.

249
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:51,440
I pray for the spreading fog

250
00:16:51,520 --> 00:16:57,360
to protect the loyal of Great Ming.

251
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:02,320
The execution supervisor has vanished!

252
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,120
Everyone, look!

253
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,520
Men of the Grand Court, hold your positions!

254
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:07,880
Protect the civilians first!

255
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:19,600
It's a deceptive illusion!

256
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:20,440
Mere posturing!

257
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:21,720
Embroidered Uniform Guard, heed my command!

258
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:22,720
Form the arrow formation!

259
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,480
Do not act rashly!

260
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:27,240
Fire!

261
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:15,280
When snow flies in the Spring City as we meet

262
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:19,080
The endless brilliance of the night

263
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:22,480
Oh, the sorrow of injustice, what can be done?

264
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:26,280
The mournful north wind never departs

265
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:30,040
New ghosts cry injustice, while old ghosts weep

266
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:33,080
I am the Snow Woman who appeases the world's injustices,

267
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:33,920
Dou E

268
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,320
I have come specifically to welcome Li Chenyang

269
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:37,840
To a land of peace

270
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:40,480
To help him be exonerated

271
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,200
Playing tricks

272
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:45,840
Mere Embroidered Uniform Guards

273
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,280
Deluding yourselves to stop us

274
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:48,960
Truly laughable

275
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:52,360
Do not chase a desperate foe

276
00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:54,760
Why won't you listen?

277
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,920
One Director of the Eastern Depot has already died

278
00:18:58,440 --> 00:18:59,840
We can't lose a Commander of the Embroidered Uniform Guard too

279
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:00,200
Let's go

280
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,000
Such impressive lightness skill

281
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,120
Audacious rebel

282
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:54,920
You shall not escape

283
00:19:58,080 --> 00:19:59,880
To be able to deduce my escape route...

284
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:00,880
You are someone of note

285
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:02,520
Goumang in the east

286
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,280
Zhurong and Houtu in the south

287
00:20:04,560 --> 00:20:05,520
Rushou in the west

288
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:06,360
Xuanming in the north

289
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:07,960
The lands illuminated by the sun and moon

290
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,520
Are the Four Directions

291
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:11,440
We come from The Four Directions

292
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:13,400
Protecting the peace of the people with our own will

293
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:15,640
The goose passes, leaving its cry, not a trace

294
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:18,080
You only need to remember the name "The Four Directions"

295
00:20:18,480 --> 00:20:19,520
Quite the organization, "The Four Directions"

296
00:20:20,120 --> 00:20:21,720
What exactly is the purpose of abducting Li Chenyang?

297
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,320
Those who understand the times

298
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:24,960
Should hand the person over at once

299
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:26,800
Understand what times?

300
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:28,120
Hand over what person?

301
00:20:28,840 --> 00:20:29,280
My Lord

302
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:31,800
Instead of chatting and admiring the moon with me here

303
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:33,560
You'd better hurry and find the person you need to find

304
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:35,400
And do the things you need to do

305
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,840
Extremely arrogant

306
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:38,880
Surrender now

307
00:21:09,600 --> 00:21:11,240
This is how the Grand Court of Justice should be

308
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,800
But you're still far from it

309
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,240
Such a vicious hidden weapon

310
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,520
It must be from the Tang Clan

311
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:49,120
Master Shen

312
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:51,760
I just found this

313
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,160
Diagram of the Four Symbols

314
00:21:57,320 --> 00:21:58,480
Who exactly are they?

315
00:21:58,840 --> 00:22:00,960
To dare openly oppose the Court and the Eastern Depot

316
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:07,160
Close the doors

317
00:22:07,320 --> 00:22:08,200
Do not let anyone enter

318
00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:09,080
Yes, sir

319
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:09,480
Shuimo

320
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,400
Notify Master Pei to gather at the front hall immediately

321
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,320
Yes, My Lord

322
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:16,680
My Lord

323
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:18,680
Regarding what happened at Xisi Archway tonight...

324
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:19,320
How should we respond?

325
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:28,960
Danqing, grind the ink

326
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:29,920
Oh

327
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:36,880
Zhang Yi

328
00:22:37,360 --> 00:22:38,360
What happened?

329
00:22:38,520 --> 00:22:39,960
Can't a man rest in the middle of the night?

330
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:40,960
Master Pei.

331
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:42,160
You're finally here.

332
00:22:42,560 --> 00:22:43,280
I'm dying to talk.

333
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,320
Two hours ago,

334
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,320
Master Zhang and I assisted the Eastern Depot and the Guard

335
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:48,160
in supervising Li Chenyang's execution at Xisi Pailou.

336
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,240
It was April in early spring,

337
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,520
yet heavy snow fell.

338
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:51,840
Stop storytelling.

339
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:53,680
Why stop?

340
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,400
Just get to the point.

341
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:57,360
But those bizarre sights...

342
00:22:57,520 --> 00:22:59,080
every part sounds like a story!

343
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,280
It feels like it's all important.

344
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:01,120
The point is,

345
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:03,640
our supervising official,

346
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:06,080
Director of the Eastern Depot, Feng Hai,

347
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,760
was assassinated during the execution.

348
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:11,440
Master Pei,

349
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:13,040
you're getting carried away with your gloating.

350
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:13,920
Bah!

351
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,440
Ignorant child.

352
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:17,760
I have worked hard all these years,

353
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:20,040
just waiting to retire and return home.

354
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:21,760
Now that this has happened,

355
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:22,880
the Grand Court of Justice

356
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,800
is like a monkey in a snare,

357
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:27,640
and is done for.

358
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:29,680
My Lord.

359
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:30,960
Feng Hai's death

360
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:32,520
cannot be blamed on our Grand Court of Justice.

361
00:23:32,560 --> 00:23:33,800
Since ancient times, it's always the third quarter of noon,

362
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:34,800
when Yang energy is at its peak, that people are executed.

363
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,240
Who ever heard of the demon hour,

364
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:37,640
when hell's gates open, for an execution?

365
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:39,320
Supervision was supposed to be the Grand Court's job,

366
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:41,040
but they insisted on doing it themselves.

367
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,040
You didn't see

368
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:43,240
the Embroidered Uniform Guard's formation today.

369
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,280
You'll see it soon enough.

370
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:46,480
Open the door!

371
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:47,360
Where is everyone?

372
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:48,480
Open up, hurry!

373
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:50,480
Is anyone inside?

374
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:51,240
Open the door!

375
00:23:51,560 --> 00:23:51,920
Zhang Yi.

376
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:54,520
How is the case file coming along?

377
00:23:54,800 --> 00:23:55,440
I just completed it.

378
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:56,400
Once the ink dries,

379
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:57,360
we can present it to His Majesty.

380
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,720
The die is cast.

381
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:04,400
We absolutely cannot hand the initiative of the investigation

382
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,440
to the Eastern Depot.

383
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:06,800
If we hand it to them,

384
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:07,640
and they fail to solve it,

385
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:10,080
they'll surely make the Grand Court of Justice the scapegoat.

386
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:13,760
You know what to do later.

387
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:15,200
Be a man with your tail between your legs,

388
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:16,360
and a dog with your head held high.

389
00:24:21,800 --> 00:24:23,320
What are you dawdling for?

390
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:30,200
Officer Song, Scribe of the Eastern Depot,

391
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:31,160
is here to condemn the Grand Court of Justice!

392
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:32,880
Are you all tired of living?

393
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:36,520
I apologize for not welcoming you sooner.

394
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,080
I apologize for not welcoming you sooner.

395
00:24:39,040 --> 00:24:41,960
Pei Yuandong of the Grand Court greets Officer Song.

396
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:44,280
Officer Song, visiting the Grand Court so late at night...

397
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:46,240
what is the reason for this visit?

398
00:24:47,360 --> 00:24:49,560
Master Pei, you are feigning ignorance.

399
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:51,640
My Eastern Depot Director, Lord Feng Hai,

400
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:53,280
was in charge of supervising Li Chenyang's execution.

401
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:54,560
Your Grand Court of Justice

402
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:56,480
only sent some twenty men to assist,

403
00:24:56,800 --> 00:24:58,760
leading to the murder of my Director.

404
00:24:59,040 --> 00:25:00,560
The criminal Li Chenyang

405
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,920
was hijacked and taken away.

406
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:04,560
Having committed such a grave dereliction of duty,

407
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:06,720
you dare ask me what I am here for?

408
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:08,000
My Lord!

409
00:25:08,080 --> 00:25:09,440
Officer Song, we are wrongly accused!

410
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,160
Heaven, earth, sun, and moon can bear witness!

411
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:13,520
The number of supervisors sent by the Grand Court today

412
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:15,440
was of the highest level.

413
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,600
It was Vice Minister Zhang Yi of the Grand Court

414
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,400
who led the team personally!

415
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,160
Towards the Eastern Depot,

416
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:23,600
I have absolutely no disrespect!

417
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:25,560
Go quickly and petition His Majesty.

418
00:25:25,560 --> 00:25:25,800
Yes.

419
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:27,920
The heaven, earth, sun, and moon of our Great Ming

420
00:25:27,920 --> 00:25:29,400
are probably the busiest of all.

421
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:30,840
All day long, for the likes of you

422
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:33,320
brainless officials, they have to vouch for you.

423
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:37,920
Where is Vice Minister Zhang Yi of the Grand Court?

424
00:25:38,040 --> 00:25:38,800
Well...

425
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:41,680
Could it be he has fled to escape punishment,

426
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:44,400
and dares not show his face?

427
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:47,560
Every word Master Pei said is true.

428
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:54,080
Vice Minister Zhang Yi of the Grand Court greets Officer Song.

429
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,160
I was delayed by a matter just now.

430
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:55,920
Please forgive me.

431
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,200
At the time of the execution,

432
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:58,480
the Director and Master Shen

433
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:00,240
ordered us to maintain order among the people outside.

434
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:01,200
Therefore,

435
00:26:01,560 --> 00:26:03,120
the Grand Court could not enter the execution platform,

436
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:05,080
and thus could not protect the Director,

437
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,040
resulting in this tragedy.

438
00:26:06,760 --> 00:26:07,400
However,

439
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:08,560
to make up for the mistake,

440
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:10,560
the Grand Court is willing to fully investigate the culprit.

441
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:14,080
My Lord,

442
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:17,240
the one who handed over Li Chenyang's case files to me

443
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:19,240
was this very person.

444
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:23,880
What a joke!

445
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:26,680
My Director has been murdered.

446
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,960
Since when is it the turn of your Grand Court,

447
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:31,120
this bunch of useless idiots, to investigate?

448
00:26:31,560 --> 00:26:34,160
My Eastern Depot will get to the bottom of this.

449
00:26:36,080 --> 00:26:37,320
You just wait

450
00:26:37,320 --> 00:26:38,920
to be sentenced together!

451
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:40,160
Officer Song,

452
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,760
please give the Grand Court

453
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:43,320
a chance to redeem itself.

454
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,960
Regarding today's events,

455
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,520
a case file has already been opened.

456
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:49,320
We will certainly give the Eastern Depot and the people

457
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,760
a satisfactory answer.

458
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:58,160
Pei Yuandong.

459
00:26:58,720 --> 00:27:00,360
Who gave you the audacity

460
00:27:00,360 --> 00:27:02,320
to petition His Majesty on your own accord?

461
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,720
Officer Song,

462
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:06,880
I did it for the sake of your reputation.

463
00:27:07,520 --> 00:27:08,480
In these critical times,

464
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:10,800
the Director has unfortunately met his end.

465
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:11,880
So many eyes

466
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:14,800
are watching you ascend to the position of Director.

467
00:27:15,560 --> 00:27:18,120
If you lead the team personally at this time,

468
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:18,840
it...

469
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:20,560
it will invite

470
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:23,400
the gossip of petty people.

471
00:27:25,280 --> 00:27:27,120
How thoughtful of you, Officer Pei.

472
00:27:27,840 --> 00:27:29,760
I have underestimated you.

473
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,840
However, what you say

474
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:35,440
is not without reason.

475
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:37,600
Pass on my order.

476
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:39,480
Lock down the capital for three days.

477
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,720
The Grand Court of Justice shall investigate

478
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:43,840
the true culprit behind the Director's murder

479
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,840
and the whereabouts of the criminal official Li Chenyang.

480
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:48,000
Shen Youzhi, Commander of the Embroidered Uniform Guard,

481
00:27:48,320 --> 00:27:50,160
shall assist the Grand Court of Justice in the investigation.

482
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,600
As you command.

483
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,160
Pei Yuandong, Zhang Yi.

484
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:54,680
I give you three days.

485
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:57,000
You must solve the case within three days.

486
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:57,920
Otherwise,

487
00:27:58,520 --> 00:28:00,360
I will take everyone in the Grand Court of Justice

488
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:02,800
to sacrifice to the Director's spirit in heaven.

489
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:09,800
Youzhi.

490
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:10,280
Here.

491
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:13,440
We used someone else to remove Feng Hai.

492
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,600
It was convenient,

493
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:15,880
but a bit risky.

494
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:18,400
Once you track down Li Chenyang's whereabouts,

495
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:19,360
execute him first and report later.

496
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,560
Kill on sight.

497
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:21,160
Yes, sir.

498
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:30,680
Lock down the city for three days.

499
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:31,920
Capture Li Chenyang!

500
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:33,080
Yes, sir!

501
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:33,840
Go!

502
00:28:33,840 --> 00:28:34,480
Search carefully!

503
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:34,920
Yes!

504
00:28:36,320 --> 00:28:39,360
Go! Move, move, move!

505
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:40,720
Over here!

506
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:44,080
Search thoroughly!

507
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:45,760
Anything over here?

508
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:46,800
Quick!

509
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,960
Over there, over there!

510
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:51,360
Search!

511
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:16,520
Kill! Kill! Kill!

512
00:29:21,120 --> 00:29:21,840
Attack!

513
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:45,480
Investigating the case today...

514
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:47,520
Where is your master?

515
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:49,840
Answering Your Honor,

516
00:29:50,360 --> 00:29:51,280
our Vice Minister

517
00:29:51,560 --> 00:29:52,440
is on his way.

518
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:53,560
He ran into some trouble.

519
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:53,920
So...

520
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:56,000
So the Grand Court's investigations are this lax.

521
00:29:56,360 --> 00:29:58,240
We, the joint investigation, have waited here for ages.

522
00:29:58,240 --> 00:29:59,160
Yet he is still not here.

523
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:01,080
What does this have to do with being lax?

524
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:02,760
Hasn't the Grand Court already

525
00:30:02,760 --> 00:30:03,880
sent people to inspect and gather evidence?

526
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:06,480
You've made all the decisions that needed making.

527
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:08,320
So what is Master Zhang supposed to do when he arrives?

528
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:10,400
The pitiful Grand Court of Justice.

529
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:12,880
Usually handling trivial cases.

530
00:30:13,080 --> 00:30:13,960
Finally stumbling upon

531
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,000
a major case for promotion and wealth,

532
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:16,520
yet they still have to rely on your whims.

533
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:17,600
Commander Yuan,

534
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:20,000
your ability to side with outsiders

535
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:20,560
is quite impressive.

536
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:22,360
You flatter me, Master Shen.

537
00:30:23,040 --> 00:30:23,880
My elbows

538
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:25,680
can't be broken just to bend them inward.

539
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:27,000
Besides,

540
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:29,360
I call this acting impartially.

541
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:30,400
Master Zhang.

542
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:32,360
Good morning, my lords.

543
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:34,120
You guys keep busy.

544
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:34,920
I'm going to grab a bite.

545
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,000
Uncle Zhang,

546
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,440
give me a bowl of sweet soy milk.

547
00:30:37,520 --> 00:30:38,200
Add two spoons of sugar.

548
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,000
One fried dough stick,

549
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:39,760
and two sweet fried cakes.

550
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,120
Coming right up!

551
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:41,560
What?

552
00:30:42,080 --> 00:30:43,600
Starting the investigation without breakfast?

553
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:44,840
Master Zhang,

554
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:46,160
I've wanted to visit you for a long time.

555
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:47,360
But alas, the Embroidered Uniform Guard

556
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:49,120
and the filthy mess at home are too much,

557
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,720
always keeping me from making friends.

558
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:53,320
Master Shen.

559
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,560
Master Zhang.

560
00:30:56,120 --> 00:30:57,000
Is the fried cake good?

561
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,000
Do you want some, Master Shen?

562
00:30:59,120 --> 00:31:00,560
Come, order whatever you want. My treat.

563
00:31:00,560 --> 00:31:01,360
Master Zhang,

564
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:02,800
please have some dignity.

565
00:31:03,320 --> 00:31:04,520
The investigation and tracking are urgent.

566
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:05,680
We don't have time

567
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,360
to critique the craft of fried cakes with you here.

568
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:08,240
Whether it's authentic or not.

569
00:31:09,280 --> 00:31:10,160
As the saying goes,

570
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:11,640
"There is only a sky you can't reach,

571
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:13,200
not a mountain you can't cross."

572
00:31:13,600 --> 00:31:14,560
When officials investigate a case,

573
00:31:14,560 --> 00:31:16,040
do they stop eating and sleeping?

574
00:31:16,200 --> 00:31:16,920
Old man,

575
00:31:17,320 --> 00:31:18,720
didn't you see a murder happened here?

576
00:31:19,440 --> 00:31:20,960
The whole city is under curfew for three days.

577
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:23,120
Who allowed you to set up a stall here?

578
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:24,480
I sell breakfast.

579
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:26,840
Did I pay less tax,

580
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:28,960
or did I commit a murder?

581
00:31:29,840 --> 00:31:30,560
Master Shen,

582
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:35,120
I advise you to calm down.

583
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:36,960
This person might be

584
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,960
a sleeper agent planted by the Eastern Depot.

585
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:45,800
Since this old man is here rain or shine,

586
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,440
always at this spot,

587
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,440
then regarding last night's murder,

588
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:51,040
did you see it clearly?

589
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:53,880
Naturally.

590
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:54,520
Uncle Zhang,

591
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:56,720
we were also at the crime scene last night.

592
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:58,760
But onlookers see more clearly than those involved.

593
00:31:59,520 --> 00:32:00,120
Why don't we

594
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:01,680
listen to what Uncle Zhang has to say?

595
00:32:03,280 --> 00:32:04,240
Uncle Zhang, tell us about it.

596
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:07,040
Thank you for your kindness, my lord.

597
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:11,120
My lords,

598
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:13,640
yesterday the execution platform was no different from usual.

599
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:15,040
It's just that the snow...

600
00:32:15,080 --> 00:32:16,120
was a bit strange.

601
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,200
Let's not deny

602
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,520
things that exist outside of common logic,

603
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,720
but rather think about how to explain

604
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:22,840
what our eyes witnessed.

605
00:32:23,560 --> 00:32:25,000
In the capital during the fourth month,

606
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:26,760
there shouldn't be snow.

607
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,440
What we saw was...

608
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,400
Spring in the capital

609
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,760
The most common sight is these willow catkins

610
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,400
Lord Shen

611
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:49,320
Lord Shen

612
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:57,040
These catkins...

613
00:32:57,840 --> 00:32:59,560
are willow catkins soaked in hallucinogenic drugs

614
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:01,760
Using the catkins as a medium,

615
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:03,680
they make people inhale the hallucinogen,

616
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,720
causing mental confusion

617
00:33:05,240 --> 00:33:07,120
Judging by the intensity of our hallucinations last night,

618
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:09,760
they likely used a specific type...

619
00:33:09,760 --> 00:33:11,280
made from poisonous fungi unique to Dali

620
00:33:31,320 --> 00:33:32,400
Cannabis leaves

621
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,040
Porcini mushrooms

622
00:33:34,840 --> 00:33:35,760
Dancing mushrooms

623
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:38,560
Fly Agaric

624
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,920
Such complexity is truly rare

625
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:46,720
A strong wind rose suddenly last night

626
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:48,760
Willow catkins drifted all over the capital

627
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:49,600
Their direction was uncontrollable

628
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:51,960
But this dosage...

629
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:53,760
would only cause mild hallucinations

630
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:57,200
To prevent the prisoner from being hijacked,

631
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:59,000
all houses were built low

632
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:00,520
The surroundings are completely visible

633
00:34:01,760 --> 00:34:02,400
The entire execution ground...

634
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,840
was strictly guarded by us

635
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,400
They had absolutely no way...

636
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,840
to increase the hallucinogen dosage at close range

637
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,320
But then how...

638
00:34:08,720 --> 00:34:09,560
did they make us see this...

639
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:11,000
concentrated, large-scale illusion?

640
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:13,000
Illusion techniques

641
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:15,080
The flying snow was willow catkins

642
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:16,200
Then what about the plum blossoms?

643
00:34:16,240 --> 00:34:17,240
The people of the entire city...

644
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,720
saw them clearly and distinctly

645
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,040
What Uncle Zhang says makes sense

646
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,600
Snow in the fourth month is absurd

647
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:24,680
Plum blossoms blooming in the fourth month...

648
00:34:25,160 --> 00:34:26,160
isn't that strange too?

649
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,320
Plum blossoms love the cold

650
00:34:40,680 --> 00:34:42,240
Naturally, they wouldn't bloom in the fourth month

651
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:44,520
But if one wants to see plum blossoms in the fourth month,

652
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,440
it is not impossible

653
00:34:46,560 --> 00:34:48,240
I remember the gardeners in the Imperial Garden...

654
00:34:49,040 --> 00:34:50,600
to let His Majesty enjoy plum blossoms during the Spring Festival,

655
00:34:51,240 --> 00:34:52,720
control the temperature and fertilizer twenty days in advance

656
00:34:52,720 --> 00:34:53,400
With careful tending,

657
00:34:53,920 --> 00:34:54,560
they always succeed

658
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:55,640
After all, failing to do so...

659
00:34:55,640 --> 00:34:57,040
is a matter that could cost them their heads

660
00:34:57,560 --> 00:34:58,000
Naturally, there wouldn't be...

661
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:58,880
any mistakes

662
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:00,440
Hijacking Li Chenyang...

663
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:01,920
is no different, is it?

664
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:05,160
Warm days hasten...

665
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,280
flowers to bloom wildly

666
00:35:07,760 --> 00:35:08,840
If they used something extremely cold...

667
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:09,880
to preserve the plum blossom branches,

668
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:12,800
and took them out of the cold...

669
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:14,880
then encountering today's weather...

670
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:16,400
and the warm breath of the person holding the flower,

671
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:17,880
they could bloom at a predetermined time

672
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,960
Releasing another type of hallucinogen...

673
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:23,520
which combines with the agent on the willow catkins...

674
00:35:25,080 --> 00:35:26,320
to intensify the hallucinations

675
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:28,040
Ingenious trickery

676
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,760
The plum blossoms in the hands of the commoners...

677
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:32,440
were obtained from a magician

678
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:33,320
My Lord

679
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:35,480
All things in the world...

680
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:38,280
are illusions born from the heart

681
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:42,920
This man is nearing forty

682
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:44,960
Those eyes have seen much of the world

683
00:35:45,160 --> 00:35:46,640
And reveal the seasoning of a wanderer

684
00:35:50,160 --> 00:35:50,800
His right hand...

685
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,960
his right hand is a prosthetic
